sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant App as 📱 App
    participant QC as QuestController [server]
    participant AC as AiClient [server]
    participant RT as routes.dialogue [ai]
    participant RD as run_dialogue [ai]
    participant G as LangGraph 노드 [ai]
    participant RC as RegionCache [ai]
    participant LC as LLMClient [ai]
    participant UP as Upstage(Solar)

    App->>QC: POST /v1/quests/{id}/dialogue<br/>{node_id, stage}
    QC->>AC: dialogue(node_id, stage, player_state)
    AC->>RT: HTTP POST /v1/dialogue<br/>{node_id, stage, player_state}
    RT->>RD: run_dialogue(node_id, stage, player_state)
    RD->>G: graph.ainvoke(DialogueState)

    Note over G: persona_inject(state) ⇒ {cache_key}
    Note over G: cache_read(state) ⇒ {cache_hit:false}
    G->>RC: context_load → get_text(node_id)
    RC-->>G: 장소 텍스트(context)
    Note over G: prompt_assemble(state) ⇒ {prompt}
    G->>LC: generate → LLMClient.generate(prompt)
    LC->>UP: chat/completions (세마포어·429 백오프)
    UP-->>LC: 대사 텍스트
    LC-->>G: response
    Note over G: cache_write(state) ⇒ {}

    G-->>RD: state{response, cache_hit}
    RD-->>RT: (response, cache_hit)
    RT-->>AC: DialogueResult
    AC-->>QC: {response, cache_hit}
    QC-->>App: 200 {response, cache_hit}
